channel.description:

well i looked around and heard some people had the same problem but didn't explained that well.. (i'm dutch and NOT THAT GOOD in english)
so i'm askin if anyone could help me ... i have very nice server... only can't get it on for public...
FREE ADMIN IF U CAN HELP ME

item.title: I can't get my server for public people (i have router) U.S ROBOITCS USR5461
item.dc:creator: @Paradise_God Paradise God
item.description:
@Paradise_God wrote:

So set up an Hamachi server, Click on the middle button(It has a triangle looking shape on the button), and Click’‘Create New Network’’

By creating the network, and giving it a password, People can then join your Hamachi newtwork, and Join your server,

As long and You have the file ‘‘Runserver’’ up and your Online on Hamachi, People can join your server.
